Interface CollectionFetch<T extends Entity<T>>

Type Parameters:
T - the entity class for which this is a collection
All Known Implementing Classes:
EntityCollection, UserCollection
public interface CollectionFetch<T extends Entity<T>>

A collection of Kinvey objects.

Used to query a collection of objects from Kinvey's appdata service.
